  "reference_number": "DPR0005",
  "remarks": "\nChoe Kwang Su has been identified by the UN Panel of Experts as a representative of Haegeumgang Trading Company. In this capacity Choe Kwang Su signed a DPRK-Mozambique military cooperation contract in violation of the prohibitions imposed by United Nations Security Council Resolutions. The contract concerned the supply of arms and arms-related material to Monte Binga, a company controlled by the Government of Mozambique.",
